comments: I thought that the lessons were gone through much too quickly, and not in much depth. I found it hard to follow along most of the time. Also, I thought the quizzes and final test were hard because we never went over the material in class. Also, there\'s not nearly enough in-class time to work on projects and ask questions.
Flies through lessons, doesn\'t take time to see where everyone is at, constantly on a time schedule which doesn\'t help at all in assessing students progress.
Awesome teacher. Very helpful, really knows Flash.
